high_descs: From the hallway go into the living room, next to the sofa.
Pick up the knife that is on the sofa.
On the sofa there is a loaf of bread, slice the bread.
Take the plate and go over to the coffee table.
Put the knife down in the plate that is on the coffetable.
After putting the knife down, turn around and face the sofa.
Pick up one slice of bread from the sofa.
Take the bread with you to the coffee table on a plate.
Put the bread down on the plate next to the knife.
Pick up the plate with the bread and knife.
Take the plate to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the plate in it.
anns.task_desc: Cut the bread on the sofa and put it on a plate, take the plate to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around to head to the lamp and turn right to reach the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the couch.
Cut the bread on the couch into slices with the knife.
Turn around and face the plate.
Put the knife on the plate on the table.
Turn around and face the sofa.
Pick up a slice of bread from the couch.
Turn around to face the plate.
Put the slice of bread on the plate next to the knife.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Walk around the diningtable and reach the microwave on the left.
Put the plate in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the slice of bread on the plate in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sofa.
Take the knife from the couch.
To find the bread on the couch.
Cut the bread into pieces using the knife on the plate.
Turn around and put the knife on the plate.
Then turn and find the bread on the sofa.
Take the bread from the couch.
Turn around and go near the plate.
Put the piece of bread on the plate.
Take the plate with bread and knife from the table.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the plate with knife and bread into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the bread on the plate and put it into the microwave.
